s with condition number $\\kappa$, we give an\nalgorithm obtaining mixing time $O(\\kappa d \\log^2\\frac{\\kappa d}{\\epsilon})$,\nimproving the prior state-of-the-art by a logarithmic factor with a\nsignificantly simpler analysis; we also show a zeroth-order algorithm attains\nthe same query complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 01:43:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 20:17:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 02:19:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 22 Oct 2021 06:25:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-25"}
