 (living room) to the unseen\nenvironment (mock warehouse) in the new dataset. In contrast, the performance\nof the object detection methods drops substantially. We also implement the\nproposed method on a real-world robot to demonstrate its usefulness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 06:04:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Oct 2020 19:11:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2021 19:21:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 20 May 2021 17:24:47 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 18:05:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-30"}
