imal with the\nbaryonic component contributing most of the radial gravitational field in the\ninner parts of the galaxy (Vmax(bar) = 0.76($\\pm$0.14)Vmax).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-13"}
